Properties.ProtectedString:
local tool = script.Parent local Fire = tool:WaitForChild("Fire")
local Settings = tool:WaitForChild("Settings") local CooldownTime = Settings.CooldownTime
local Debounce = false
local Player = game:GetService("Players").LocalPlayer
local function Swing() if not Debounce then Debounce = true Fire:FireServer() wait(CooldownTime.Value) Debounce = false end end
tool.Activated:Connect(Swing)

local tool = script.Parent local Handle = tool.Handle local Fire = tool.Fire
local Settings = tool.Settings local Damage = Settings.Damage local SwingTime = Settings.SwingTime
local Lethal = false
local function ToggleLethal() if not Lethal then Lethal = true Handle.Slash:Play() Handle.Color = Color3.fromRGB(255,0,0) wait(SwingTime.Value) Handle.Color = Color3.fromRGB(163, 162, 165) Lethal = false end end
Fire.OnServerEvent:Connect(ToggleLethal)
Handle.Touched:Connect(function(hit) if Lethal == true then if hit.Parent and hit.Parent:FindFirstChild("Humanoid") then local Hum = hit.Parent:FindFirstChild("Humanoid") Handle.Hit:Play() Hum:TakeDamage(Damage.Value) end end end)
